messageBody:
> From: kms_junit [mailto:kms_junit@...]

> ...The size() method will only tell me how many hash
> values there are.

Huh?

The size() method will tell you how many objects there are
in the collection.

If you violate the contract for equals() and hashcode() (not
making them consistent), all bets are off regarding the
contracts supported by collection classes.

Daniel
